## Project based on: https://github.com/rwanrooy/TTGO-PAXCOUNTER-LoRa32-V2.1-TTN.

In honour of Martin Cooper and Arlene Harris and their vision of IoP, The Internet of People, in MediaLab_ LPWAN, we wanted to develop an IoT device that could improve the quality of the Polytechnic School of Engineering of GijÃ³n. As a result, the idea of the Cooper Sensor came in as a LoRa device that could be left without any need of mantainance measuring the water level of San Miguel's creek.

Specifically, in 2018, a major flood took place turning useless many expensive equipment from the lower floors that were used by the students during the laboratory practices of many subjetcs:
